{"summary": "The apartment is a spacious 75 m² unit located in a residential area of Bratislava with plenty of greenery and civic amenities. It has been recently renovated with new electrical wiring, plastering, windows, doors, flooring (except for the preserved parquet floors), and blinds. The kitchen is particularly noteworthy due to its size and modern appliances including an induction stove, built-in oven, extractor hood, dishwasher, refrigerator with freezer, and washing machine. The living room has been reconfigured to include space for a dining table and features a high-quality gray corner sofa bed. There are two bedrooms: one with a large wardrobe and the other with parquet flooring and carpeting. The bathroom includes a shower enclosure and LED-lit mirror. The apartment is fully furnished, including all appliances and furniture as shown in photos. It comes with a cellar and access to shared bicycle storage. Current costs for utilities (for 2 people) are approximately 170 € OSBD, 35 € electricity, and 25 € UPC internet/TV. The building is an insulated apartment complex without an elevator at the moment but plans for balcony reconstruction with stainless steel railings and frosted glass are underway. It's situated on the third floor of a five-story building, oriented to the south and west, offering quick access to public transport, schools, kindergartens, grocery stores, sports centers, and both Bratislava and Košice bypasses. The apartment is available for immediate move-in."}
